[SN]TITLE[SN]
Drivers warned of icy roads as weather warning issued

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Drivers have been warned roads could be icy as overnight rain and sleet could wash salt off treated roads.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Met Office has issued a yellow "be aware" warning for ice for the whole of Wales.
The warning runs from 20:00 GMT on Thursday until 10:00 on Friday.
Sleet and snow has been forecast over high ground and temperatures are expected to fall below freezing overnight.
